These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
House: victorian, farmhouse, art-deco, ranch-style, craftsman, cottage, tower
7 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, chess, monopoly, snooker, backgammon, billiard
The people have 7 different hobbies: hiking, cooking, singing, skydiving, magic-tricks, card-games, sudoku
 1. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
 2. the person playing snooker is the ranch-style house##1
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person playing chess##1
 4. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 5. the victorian house is on the right of the tower house##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the person playing chess##1
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the cottage house##2
 9. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the person playing canasta is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the art-deco house##1
14. the cottage house is the person who's hobby is singing##1
15. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the tower house##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the art-deco house##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the craftsman house##1
19. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
| House   | farmhouse | ranch-style         | tower   | victorian | cottage    | craftsman | art-deco |
| Game         | chess | snooker | canasta | mah-jongg | billiard  | backgammon  | monopoly    |
| Hobby     | magic-tricks  | card-games         | hiking     | cooking    | singing | skydiving     | sudoku     |

