The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: azalea, dahlia, begonia, iris, daisy, bellflower, aconite
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, disco, indie, metal, pop, reggae, rock
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, action, time-travel, family, epic, scientific
 1. the russian is the person who growsiris##1
 2. the argentine is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 3. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the dutch##1
 4. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 6. the indian is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is the indonesian##1
 8. the fan of rock is the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the indian##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the person who growsaconite##2
11. the fan of disco is the person who growsiris##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the person who growsaconite and the fan of reggae##2
14. the indonesian is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
15. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
16. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
17. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the turkish##1
18. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
19. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
20. the person who growsbegonia is between the person watching epic movies and the person who growsdahlia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7     |
